---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import ServiceExplore from '../../components/ServiceExplore.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Invisalign Treatment — Oasis Dental Care, Huntington Beach"
  description="Invisalign clear aligner treatment in Huntington Beach. Nearly invisible, removable aligners with Dr. Jason Fu. Call (714) 893-2106."
  page="services"
>

<section class="phero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="crumbs"><a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span><a href="/services">Services</a><span class="sep">/</span><span style="color:#cfe6e2">Invisalign Treatment</span></div>
    <span class="tag">Orthodontic treatment</span>
    <h1>Invisalign Treatment</h1>
    <p>Straighten your smile your way—nearly invisible and removable.</p>
    <div class="acts">
      <a class="btn" href="/contact">Book a consultation <svg class="ico" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg></a>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="tel:7148932106">Call (714) 893-2106</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="pad">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="split">
      <div>

        <div class="img-ph reveal">
          <div class="img-ph-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="3"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="9" r="1.5"/><path d="m21 15-5-5L5 21"/></svg></div>
          <span class="img-ph-lbl">Photo placeholder</span>
          <span class="img-ph-desc">Patient holding Invisalign aligner and smiling</span>
        </div>

        <div class="prose reveal">
          <span class="tag">Overview</span>
          <h2>Clear aligners built around your lifestyle.</h2>
          <p>Invisalign uses a series of clear, custom-made plastic aligners to gently move your teeth into their ideal position. Unlike metal braces, aligners are nearly invisible and removable.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="prose reveal" style="margin-top:48px">
          <h3>How Invisalign Works</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>iTero digital scan—no messy impressions</li>
            <li>Custom aligners fabricated from your scan</li>
            <li>Wear each set ~1–2 weeks, progressing to the next</li>
            <li>Check-ins with Dr. Fu to track progress</li>
          </ul>

          <div class="img-ph reveal">
            <div class="img-ph-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="3"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="9" r="1.5"/><path d="m21 15-5-5L5 21"/></svg></div>
            <span class="img-ph-lbl">Photo placeholder</span>
            <span class="img-ph-desc">Invisalign aligners on tray, or patient inserting aligner</span>
          </div>

          <h3>Invisalign vs. Traditional Braces</h3>
          <p>Aligners can be removed when eating, brushing, or flossing—making oral hygiene easier. They're nearly invisible and generally more comfortable than metal brackets and wires. Traditional braces may still be the right choice for more complex cases; we'll discuss both options.</p>

          <div class="img-ph reveal">
            <div class="img-ph-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="3"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="9" r="1.5"/><path d="m21 15-5-5L5 21"/></svg></div>
            <span class="img-ph-lbl">Photo placeholder</span>
            <span class="img-ph-desc">Side-by-side comparison or patient lifestyle shot — eating, smiling</span>
          </div>

          <h3>Who Is It For?</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Teens and adults with mild to moderate crowding or spacing</li>
            <li>Patients who want a discreet orthodontic option</li>
            <li>People who have relapsed after previous orthodontic treatment</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>At Oasis</h3>
          <p>We're an Invisalign provider in Huntington Beach. Every case begins with a digital scan and a conversation about your goals—no pressure, just options.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal" style="margin-top:48px">
          <span class="tag">Common questions</span>
          <h2 class="prose" style="margin-top:8px">Good to know.</h2>
          <div class="faq">
            <details open><summary>How long does Invisalign treatment take?</summary><p>Treatment length varies but typically ranges from 6 to 18 months depending on your specific needs. Invisalign Express offers faster treatment for minor adjustments.</p></details>
            <details><summary>Are Invisalign aligners comfortable?</summary><p>Yes! They are made from smooth, BPA-free plastic designed to fit snugly and gently move your teeth, causing minimal discomfort compared to traditional braces.</p></details>
            <details><summary>Can I eat and drink with Invisalign?</summary><p>It's best to remove your aligners when eating or drinking anything other than water to avoid staining and damage.</p></details>
            <details><summary>How often do I need to wear the aligners?</summary><p>For best results, wear your aligners 20 to 22 hours per day, removing them only to eat, brush, and floss.</p></details>
            <details><summary>Will Invisalign affect my speech?</summary><p>Most patients adapt quickly, and any temporary lisp typically disappears within a few days.</p></details>
            <details><summary>How often will I need check-ins during treatment?</summary><p>You'll have periodic visits—usually every 6 to 8 weeks—so we can monitor your progress and provide your next set of aligners. These appointments are quick and comfortable, and they help ensure your treatment stays on track.</p></details>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <aside>
        <div class="scard reveal">
          <div class="hd"><div class="grid-ov"></div><h3>Book an Invisalign consultation</h3><p>Consultations include a digital scan</p></div>
          <div class="bd">
            <div class="row"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M12 7v5l3 2"/></svg><span>Consultation typically 45–60 min</span></div>
            <div class="row"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg><span>Many insurance plans cover orthodontics</span></div>
            <div class="row"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2 4 5v6c0 5 3.5 9 8 11 4.5-2 8-6 8-11V5l-8-3z"/></svg><span>Digital precision—no impressions needed</span></div>
            <div class="divider"></div>
            <a class="btn" href="/contact">Book an Invisalign Consultation</a>
            <a class="btn btn-out" href="tel:7148932106" style="justify-content:center">Call (714) 893-2106</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<ServiceExplore />

</Layout>
